flowchart LR
    Operator[Operator]
    Odoo[Odoo control plane]
    RepoRegistry[Odoo repository registry]
    API[FastAPI Deployment API]
    ApiDb[(API PostgreSQL)]
    Node[Deployment Host]
    Doodba[/srv/doodba workspaces]
    Secrets[/srv/secrets]
    GitAgg[gitaggregate]
    Compose[Docker Compose]
    Nginx[nginx + Certbot]
    OdooInstance[Running Odoo Instance]

    Operator --> Odoo
    Odoo --> RepoRegistry
    Odoo -- manifest YAML --> API
    API --> ApiDb
    API -- SSH/Fabric --> Node
    Node --> Doodba
    Node --> Secrets
    Node --> GitAgg
    Node --> Compose
    Node --> Nginx
    Compose --> OdooInstance
    Nginx --> OdooInstance
